# Ship the research-workspace enforcement kit (the `sci-adk init-session` payload)
# as package data. `graft` recurses the whole tree INCLUDING dotfiles -- the kit
# has a hidden `.claude/` dir (hooks, settings.json, output style, /research
# command); plain globs skip dotfiles, `graft` does not. Pairs with
# include-package-data=true + package-data in pyproject.toml.
graft src/sci_adk/templates
